"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641482774,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"aJjKhpJRiRjyVg7DM8f9LUezmB0Zsk2kjEF93rjKWa8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xc31350Dd7a02f146E03c47CD34682cd541E7f2F8\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dzQjyX3UDgH2htcB2lwNjNoANtFtPFi_uxKr320_G00\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fbSoE4yt5pFt2Vzu4LnIn7XzRoZ1Sgw2ALmTkRyAFCQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"z88XGHgjKgfdvMmJLap22BudtbuKSTtb49v6DpIpXRYtuZVkyIrw_CK0kVM6OF0_M8gbB4CWCPaKoNjC54jdKw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc9264ab2bc9a8d38913c110d0aa301a31189a6a65f11e6db1dcdbf445596bc2625c085c2f66339a81b45007c6bc0c4bf42a711f6cfc7d856f843da24a181dc611c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dzQjyX3UDgH2htcB2lwNjNoANtFtPFi_uxKr320_G00\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fbSoE4yt5pFt2Vzu4LnIn7XzRoZ1Sgw2ALmTkRyAFCQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi